{"tid":1323273,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：我之前借助罵泛民左膠雙非人水貨客來激起本土社運的鬥志，在政壇做了損傷和分化","createTime":"2019-07-16T07:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T09:42:17.000Z","uid":171273,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"018c7c8f8e99cbbeea5b3a3088673dc8d80ac61f","tid":1323273,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:42:48.000Z","msg":"陳雲：憲政民主之後，我要退隱的了，因為我之前借助罵泛民左膠雙非人水貨客來激起本土社運的鬥志，在政壇做了損傷和分化，憲政民主之後就要給其他新人做我的角色了。否則我會變成革命勝利之後的孫中山，禍國殃民。<br />\n即是說，各位見到的政治陳雲（2010年&mdash;？），在香港憲政民主實現之後就會消失。各位就忍耐我的壞脾氣多一陣啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c413ee8d17a3ab57ffa4d3d1457dba39d02035","tid":1323273,"uid":171273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:44:53.000Z","msg":"佢原意係咪自己講得咁偉大都好<br />\n<br />\n連陳雲呢d私怨撚都覺得泛民開始成氣候 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0128915154914e0d267610a46f6bb6438bc815c","tid":1323273,"uid":171273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf0884fce705a0f4d74ca720c23e74e9911ba8a","tid":1323273,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:45:34.000Z","msg":"陳雲泛民和解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b548d5c7530a3cdb20bbb9bb75f7f27d6c495039","tid":1323273,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2972e5284877c6637e0b4b4b36c01fce701ac9c","tid":1323273,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d946db5b2680080ee2152c68052afa87aa01661d","tid":1323273,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT